    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS to achieve its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak mechanical integrity. The suspension geometry remains true, and the chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue. With flawless paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear, this is a turn-key example for the most discerning collector.",
