    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in paintwork that retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing, and the original carpets have been protected since day one. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed at authorized dealerships. From the flawless alloy wheels to the untouched engine bay, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. Included are all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual set, and the original window sticker. For the buyer who demands perfection and refuses to settle for anything less than a time-capsule quality example, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
