    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and free of any discernible wear, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most sophisticated buyer. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless mechanical synchronization, has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for automotive excellence.",
