    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks like it just stepped out of a time capsule. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and treated it like royalty, so the paint is flawless and the interior is still crisp. It drives like a total dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
