    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a concours-level preservation of BMW\u2019s S54 high-revving engineering. The 3.2L inline-six maintains peak compression across all cylinders, with the individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system operating with factory-spec precision. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The exterior retains its original deep luster with zero panel gaps or oxidation, while the cabin features flawless Nappa leather bolsters and a crack-free dashboard. A mechanically transparent, collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
